  "detailed_description": "Mission in Snowdriftland - Snowlogue is the free to play version of Mission in Snowdriftland. Play the first 3 levels for free.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>Chaos at the headquarters of the video game organization, UPIXO: the villain, El Pix, has stolen some important and historically valuable artifacts of video game history from the archive.<br>Help Chubby retrieve all the artifacts from El Pix's icy realm of Snowdriftland!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/28aedf0e6f6ab9960adc9195df55e791.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=296 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME CONCEPT</h2>Mission in Snowdriftland is unique in its concept:<br>Play it like a traditional Advent calendar, and select a level every day and let Chubby guide you through the cold winter days. Or play it like a classic platformer - any time you want.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/949d791562d0edc08235405a577c89e2.poster.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/949d791562d0edc08235405a577c89e2.webm?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/949d791562d0edc08235405a577c89e2.mp4?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUITABLE FOR ALL</h2>Mission in Snowdriftland offers the right gaming experience for all players: younger and less experienced gamers can get off to a quick and easy start and jump right in to start searching for the artifacts, while core gamers will face a cool challenge as they collect all 24 snowflakes per level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/12c5a3317d4b0793f342d4c3f28315a8.poster.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/12c5a3317d4b0793f342d4c3f28315a8.webm?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/12c5a3317d4b0793f342d4c3f28315a8.mp4?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/43b2d680cd46e928302a272c1cb0ea11.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=206 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAZY WORLDS</h2>Prepare to confront some wacky opponents like brightly colored penguins and polar bear joggers listening to music!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/4996ec31221fabf3e56d34e84f44dbf8.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=206 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 levels<br></li><li>Pixel art<br></li><li>Retro music<br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>Speedrun timer <br></li><li>Achievements</li></ul><br><strong>Chubby is on another mission...<i>will you join him?</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/08dcf0567e945e655bfe92371f4fa1a3.poster.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/08dcf0567e945e655bfe92371f4fa1a3.webm?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/08dcf0567e945e655bfe92371f4fa1a3.mp4?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
